pageProduct.description:
General Information

Collagen and Biotin for that every day glow.

BEAUTY BEGINS WITHIN
It's time you turn the way you think about beauty upside down, or perhaps inside out. Collagen is one of the key building blocks of our skin that helps keep it smooth, plump and glowing. However, as the years go by our body's natural production of collagen depletes and we start to see those signs of skin ageing.

WHY POP SUP?
Top-up your hair, skin and nails routine with a daily dose of 500mg Collagen and Biotin SUP.

- Support skin health
- Reduce brittle and splitting nails
- Support shiny, healthy hair POPSUP

Size: 60 Tablets

KEY FEATURES

• Support skin health
• Reduce brittle and splitting nails
• Support shiny, healthy hair

Warnings

If symptons persist talk to your health professional. Do not use product if tamper evident seal is damaged. Reseal immediately after use.

CONTAINS FISH PRODUCT

Ingredients

Hydrolysed collagen 500mg
Biotin 2.5mg

Contains: CONTAINS FISH PRODUCT

Allergen Contains: Fish

Allergen Free From: Dairy| Gluten

Directions

Take 1 tablet daily

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C
